6 ## Architecture
7
8 Three-layer CLI: `cli.ts` dispatches to command handlers (`src/commands/`),
which orchestrate
9 feature modules (`src/features/<name>/`). Each feature is self-contained wit
h `*.feature.ts`
(definition), `*.preview.ts` (compute planned changes), `*.detect.ts` (detec
t/audit), and
`*.apply.ts` (write changes). The `src/lib/feature-preview/` layer is shared
infrastructure for
previewing, diffing, and applying file changes. `src/lib/audit/` holds the n
ew cross-feature
audit utility. `src/lib/prompts/` holds reusable prompt helpers. Shared CLI
primitives come from
`@finografic/cli-kit`.
