## Stack
17
Runtime: `@finografic/cli-kit`, `@clack/prompts`, `execa`, `picocolors`, `@f
inografic/deps-policy`,
`@finografic/core`. Build: `tsdown`. Test: `vitest`. Lint/format: `oxlint`,
