## Schema / Types
23
- `Feature` — definition with `id`, `label`, `detect?`, `audit?`, `apply`
- `AuditStatus` — `'installed' | 'partial' | 'missing'` (new, 2026-04-26)
- `AuditResult` — `{ status: AuditStatus; detail?: string }`
- `FeatureContext` — `{ targetDir: string }`
- `FeaturePreviewResult` — array of `FeaturePreviewChange` (write or delete)
- `FeatureApplyResult` — `{ applied, noopMessage?, error?, appliedTargetPath
s? }`
- `PackageJson` — typed subset used by oxc-config canonical transforms
31
## CLI Commands
33
| Command      | Description                                              |
| ------------ | -------------------------------------------------------- |
| create       | Scaffold a new @finografic package from templates        |
| migrate      | Sync conventions to an existing package (dry-run by default
) |
| deps         | Sync devDependencies to @finografic/deps-policy versions |
| features     | Add optional features to an existing package             |
| audit        | Scan features, show installed/partial/missing, apply select
ed |
| update-self  | Self-update genx to latest                               |
