## Decisions
44
1. Registry order in `feature-registry.ts` is the canonical sort order for a
ll feature prompts (2026-04-26)
2. `audit()` on Feature is optional; fallback is `detect()` → binary `instal
led | missing` (2026-04-26)
3. `partial` = primary indicator present (package in devDeps / file exists)
but preview still has changes (2026-04-26)
4. `applyFeaturesToTarget` exported from `features.cli.ts` (not extracted to
lib) — single consumer still (2026-04-26)
